le. It delicately kills the germs by its smoother affect and also protects the sensitive skin from turning black and dry. Even severe rashes can be dealt with a regular use of rash cream that makes baby skin soft, supple and free of germs.<\/p>\n<p>Before attending this meet up, I didn\u2019t know how important are the first few months of a child. I\u2019m grateful to have learned this at the right time for the right growth and health.<\/p>\n<p>I, now convey this over to my readers to learn and implement these preventive measures when life calls for it.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I attended a seminar on the health and hygiene of children. Which was informative and created awareness about the importance<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":11947,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[18],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11944"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11944"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11944\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":11946,"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11944\/revisions\/11946"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/11947"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/coolandcool.inventivemind.com.pk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11944"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":tr